headline: Trump just gave a new signal he isn't going to let up on Big Tech
summary: President-elect Donald Trump is making it clear he doesn't intend to ease up on the nation's technology giants once he is back in the Oval Office.

headline: Three Reasons We Are Fans of Airbnb (ABNB)
summary: Since June 2024, Airbnb has been in a holding pattern, posting a small loss of 4.5% while floating around $139.19. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 13.7% gain during that period.
